{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about","content_id":"a07df2ba-905e-4bcf-bab7-2898de5400e4","description":"UK Fusion Energy (UKFE) will lead the delivery of the STEP programme to design and build the UK’s first prototype fusion energy plant. ","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>UK Fusion Energy (UKFE), a wholly owned subsidiary of the UK Atomic Energy Authority (UKAEA) Group, will lead the delivery of the STEP programme to design and build the UK’s first prototype fusion energy plant. </p>\n\n<p>STEP will be built at West Burton, a former coal-fired power station site in Nottinghamshire, and aims to demonstrate net energy from fusion in the 2040s.  <br>\n <br>\nOur industrial model will combine the best of public and private sectors in an integrated alliance to deliver the STEP prototype fusion plant, with UKAEA as fusion partner alongside an engineering partner and construction partner.  <br>\n <br>\nTogether with our partners, we will leverage the UK’s renowned status in fusion research and development to lead the delivery of a fusion sector that will help meet global energy demand in the second half of this century.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-mission-and-values\">Our mission and values</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"we-are-pioneering\">We are pioneering</h3>\n\n<p>We are bold in our thinking, embrace innovation, and act with courage. We challenge norms, explore the unconventional, and strive for solutions.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"we-deliver\">We deliver</h3>\n\n<p>As we evolve, we maintain a delivery mindset, staying focused and aligned with programme goals. We ensure optimal and timely delivery through efficient operations.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"we-champion-safety\">We champion safety</h3>\n\n<p>We prioritise physical safety, making it fundamental in all our choices, fostering a culture of accountability and diligence with a safety-oriented approach.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"we-all-matter\">We all matter</h3>\n\n<p>We embody compassion, care for ourselves, colleagues, and those we engage with, embrace uniqueness, and promote inclusivity.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"we-embrace-change\">We embrace change</h3>\n\n<p>We are adaptable and resilient, open to learning and evolving. We maintain balance in facing challenges, upholding well-being, unity, and efficiency.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"we-act-as-one\">We act as one</h3>\n\n<p>We foster a collective mindset through shared commitment, collaboration, and honest, transparent dealings, ensuring effective cooperation to achieve goals.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:42:47Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[{"contents":["63fbccfd-4167-429a-a5f9-dd0aa2160c91",{"title":"Jobs","url":"https://stepfusion.com/careers/"}],"name":"Jobs and contracts"}],"headers":[{"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are"},{"headers":[{"id":"we-are-pioneering","level":3,"text":"We are pioneering"},{"id":"we-deliver","level":3,"text":"We deliver"},{"id":"we-champion-safety","level":3,"text":"We champion safety"},{"id":"we-all-matter","level":3,"text":"We all matter"},{"id":"we-embrace-change","level":3,"text":"We embrace change"},{"id":"we-act-as-one","level":3,"text":"We act as one"}],"id":"our-mission-and-values","level":2,"text":"Our mission and values"}],"organisation":"e2193247-d27f-4509-b0ae-45abbc391cc1","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2026-03-17T08:42:47+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-fusion-energy/about","content_id":"a07df2ba-905e-4bcf-bab7-2898de5400e4","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-17T08:42:47Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"htt